    post:
      x-skaffolder-ignore: true
      summary: Login API
      security: []

        - Security
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                username:
                  type: string
                password:
                  type: string

                username: admin

                token:
                  type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/User"

      x-skaffolder-ignore: true

                  type: string
                passwordOld:
                  type: string

        "200":
